===Main drops===

The probability for a player to receive some [[coal]] depends on the player's mining level. The rock will deplete after receiving the [ore], unless affected by the effect of [[Mining gloves|standard]] or [[Expert mining gloves|expert mining gloves]].

{{DropsTableHead}}
