The chance of successfully mining a coal rock varies from 16/256 at level 1 (if such a thing were possible), up to 100/256 at level 99.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1407009871564840964|quote=Coal: 6.3% - 39.2%.|date=21 June 2021|archiveurl=https://archive.is/V0eDD|archivedate=21 June 2021}}

